{"art": [], "author": [{"email_address": "annabruzgulispolitifact@gmail.com", "first_name": "Anna", "id": 484, "last_name": "Bruzgulis", "name_slug": "anna-bruzgulis", "on_staff_page": null, "phone": null, "photo": null, "publication": {"id": 1, "publication_name": "PolitiFact", "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/publication/1/"}, "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/staffer/484/", "title": "PolitiFact Illinois correspondent", "twitter": null}], "canonical_url": "/truth-o-meter/statements/2015/nov/10/donald-trump/trump-says-trade-imbalance-between-us-and-china-to/", "edition": {"adkey": "Editions", "advalue": "National", "edition": "National", "edition_slug": "truth-o-meter", "has_afterthefact": false, "id": 1, "index_page": true, "meter_name": "The Truth-O-Meter<sup>TM</sup>", "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/edition/1/"}, "editor": [{"email_address": "asharockman@politifact.com", "first_name": "Aaron", "id": 114, "last_name": "Sharockman", "name_slug": "aaron-sharockman", "on_staff_page": 2, "phone": "727-553-4534", "photo": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/static.politifact.com/politifact/staffers/zwPolitifactHeadshots05.JPG", "publication": {"id": 1, "publication_name": "PolitiFact", "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/publication/1/"}, "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/staffer/114/", "title": "Executive Director", "twitter": "asharock"}], "facebook_headline": null, "id": 11550, "in_future": false, "is_pundit": false, "make_public": true, "preview": true, "researcher": [{"email_address": "annabruzgulispolitifact@gmail.com", "first_name": "Anna", "id": 484, "last_name": "Bruzgulis", "name_slug": "anna-bruzgulis", "on_staff_page": null, "phone": null, "photo": null, "publication": {"id": 1, "publication_name": "PolitiFact", "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/publication/1/"}, "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/staffer/484/", "title": "PolitiFact Illinois correspondent", "twitter": null}], "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/statement/11550/", "ruling": {"adkey": "Truth-O-Meter", "advalue": "Mostly False", "id": 4, "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/statementruling/4/", "ruling": "Mostly False", "ruling_graphic": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/static.politifact.com/rulings/tom-mostlyfalse.png", "ruling_slug": "barely-true"}, "ruling_comments": "<p>Donald Trump turned a question about the Trans-Pacific Partnership into an opportunity to discuss the United States&rsquo; trade deficit with China during the Nov. 10, 2015, Fox Business debate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For the record, the TPP involves Asian nations, but not China.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Still, Trump said that &quot;We&rsquo;re losing now over $500 billion a year in terms of imbalance with China.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Last month at a campaign rally in Sioux Falls, Iowa<strong>, </strong>Trump said &quot;we have almost a $400 billion trade imbalance with China.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A jump of more than $100 billion in less than a month? Really?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We reached out to Trump&rsquo;s campaign for more information on the figure, but did not hear back. However, according to data from the Census Bureau, the U.S. trade deficit with China clocked in at $343 billion in 2014. That makes Trump off by more than 31 percent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For comparison, a $343 billion trade gap is roughly the <a href=\"http://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GDP.MKTP.CD?order=wbapi_data_value_2014+wbapi_data_value+wbapi_data_value-last&amp;sort=asc\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><u>entire Gross Domestic Product of Denmark</u></a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So far, the trade deficit for 2015 has been calculated through September 2015, totalling<strong> </strong>almost $274 billion.<strong> </strong>Over the <a href=\"https://www.census.gov/foreign-trade/balance/c5700.html#2014\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><u>last 12 months of available data,</u></a> the trade deficit has totaled $364 billion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That&rsquo;s a big deficit but not more than $500 billion as Trump said.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since 1986, the yearly U.S. trade deficit with China has grown from year to year except in 2001 and 2009. See our <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1BMZ0sqDf7tvLxZFXzQAmqVyzNcBsx42CFG1mTP2Gvsk/edit?usp=sharing\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><u>chart</u></a> for more information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our ruling</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trump said that &quot;we&rsquo;re losing now over $500 billion a year in terms of imbalance with China.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Last month, Trump said almost $400 billion during a speech in Iowa. He should have stuck to that figure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 2014 trade deficit totaled $343 billion, and it&rsquo;s expected to be larger in 2015 but not more than $500 billion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trump&rsquo;s claim rates Mostly False.</p>\r\n", "ruling_comments_date": "2015-11-10T22:29:41.395078", "ruling_date": "2015-11-10T22:44:21", "ruling_headline": "Trump says that trade imbalance between U.S. and China tops $500B", "ruling_headline_slug": "trump-says-trade-imbalance-between-us-and-china-to", "ruling_link_text": "Inflating the number", "ruling_state": null, "source_documents": null, "sources": "<p>Google Sheets, &quot;<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1BMZ0sqDf7tvLxZFXzQAmqVyzNcBsx42CFG1mTP2Gvsk/edit#gid=0\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><u>Trade Deficit Since 1985</u></a>,&quot; Nov. 8, 2015</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C-SPAN, &quot;<a href=\"http://www.c-span.org/video/?329010-1/donald-trump-campaign-rally-sioux-city-iowa&amp;start=534\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><u>Donald Trump Campaign Rally in Sioux City, Iowa</u></a>,&quot; Oct. 27, 2015</p>\r\n\r\n<p>U.S. Census Bureau, &quot;<a href=\"https://www.census.gov/foreign-trade/balance/c5700.html#2014\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><u>Trade in Goods with China</u></a>,&quot; accessed Nov. 8, 2015</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The World Bank, &quot;<a href=\"http://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GDP.MKTP.CD?order=wbapi_data_value_2014+wbapi_data_value+wbapi_data_value-last&amp;sort=asc\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><u>GDP (current US$)</u></a>,&quot; accessed Nov. 9, 2015</p>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n", "speaker": {"adkey": "People ", "advalue": "Trump", "barely_true_count": 134, "current_job": "President", "false_count": 210, "first_name": "Donald", "half_true_count": 92, "home_state": "New York", "id": 1019, "last_name": "Trump", "mostly_true_count": 72, "name_slug": "donald-trump", "pants_count": 91, "party": {"id": 3, "party": "Republican", "party_slug": "republican", "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/party/3/"}, "photo": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/static.politifact.com/politifact/mugs/NYT_TRUMP_CAMPAIGN_5.jpg", "primary_edition": {"adkey": "Editions", "advalue": "National", "edition": "National", "edition_slug": "truth-o-meter", "has_afterthefact": false, "id": 1, "index_page": true, "meter_name": "The Truth-O-Meter<sup>TM</sup>", "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/edition/1/"}, "promise_meter_cutout": null, "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/person/1019/", "total_count": 645, "true_count": 29, "website": "https://www.donaldjtrump.com/"}, "statement": "<p>&quot;We&rsquo;re losing now over $500 billion a year in terms of imbalance with China.&quot;</p>\r\n", "statement_context": "a debate in Milwaukee, Wis.", "statement_date": "2015-11-10", "statement_type": {"id": 2, "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/statementtype/2/", "statement_type": "Claim", "type_description": "blog post "}, "subject": [{"description": "", "id": 180, "photo": null, "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/subject/180/", "subject": "China", "subject_slug": "china", "used_in_edition": ["/api/v/2/edition/10/"]}, {"description": "", "id": 27, "photo": null, "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/subject/27/", "subject": "Foreign Policy", "subject_slug": "foreign-policy", "used_in_edition": []}, {"description": "", "id": 143, "photo": null, "resource_uri": "/api/v/2/subject/143/", "subject": "Trade", "subject_slug": "trade", "used_in_edition": []}], "target": [], "twitter_headline": ""}